research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Palouse, WA operates under a Mayor-Council government type. The elected officials include the Mayor and six City Council members. One council seat (Seat 7) is currently vacant. The name 'Daniel Mullendore' is used for Seat 2, as found on the City Council Members page, while 'Danny Mullendore' is also present on the Government page. William Slinkard is listed as holding Seat 4 as of January 1, 2026.
